Alembic migrations for OLT Manager (Phase 1+).

Usage:

    export DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@host/oltmanager_dev
    cd backend
    alembic upgrade head     # apply all pending migrations
    alembic downgrade -1     # roll back one
    alembic revision -m "..." --autogenerate  # generate next migration

Migration tree:

    0001_baseline                — full pre-Phase-1 schema (19 tables)
    0002_tenants_and_workspaces  — Tenant + Workspace + user_workspaces
    0003_add_tenant_id           — denormalize tenant_id onto every table
                                   + bootstrap-tenant backfill, then NOT NULL,
                                   plus unique-constraint reshuffles
    0004_rls                     — Postgres Row-Level Security policies

Each migration's `downgrade()` is the inverse, so any phase can be rolled
back without losing data.
